 7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the italian is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the fan of soul is the police-officer##1
10. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |      3      |
